{"tid":1632282,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"其實連登係咪淪陷左","createTime":"2019-10-06T17:27:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T21:59:38.000Z","uid":288058,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a5f5c63eda2a7b75329ac79e528260c550c7df4c","tid":1632282,"uid":288058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:27:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">以前一有負能量，上下連登見到大家好有heart即刻舒服晒<br />\n<br />\n依家打開連登，全部都係屌手足或者飛機post（有時行動post都冇埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n香港人已經唔可以再輸啦 係咪又想返返去2014年咁？<br />\n<br />\n大家冷靜少少<br />\n<br />\n講嘢檢點啲 唔好意見不合就亂咁屌人<br />\n<br />\n我知大家都好燥但係你屌完人有乜幫助呢？<br />\n<br />\n不完美 有改善空間<br />\n<br />\n希望大家理智少少 無忘初衷 記住天琦嘅嗰句說話<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">齊上齊落 <br />\n兄弟爬山 <br />\n槍口對外 <br />\n五毛死全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"69e029fb3b5e4639d83bb7fed87070c3a2320c04","tid":1632282,"uid":288058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:30:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">支持但不沉迷鶳 對準但唔太過勤力裝修<br />\n唔好將責任推比文宣組</span></span>"},{"pid":"dc9e23582674d87a5a63f1e7bbbfa3a950279ba4","tid":1632282,"uid":288058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:30:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">拒絕分化 篤灰</span>"},{"pid":"51694c167ccce76de896d11bf21cb4819d12a06b","tid":1632282,"uid":288058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:31:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">理性討論 <br />\n不人身攻擊</span>"},{"pid":"932d7f8cc6fbcf2af652fcf7340b885940aa3591","tid":1632282,"uid":288058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:31:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">做得好就賀一賀佢<br />\n做得差就主動承認</span>"},{"pid":"b429d430534f62cd0032bf91403c8993e8f1d979","ti